h4><p>Every design decision, product and certificate recorded from day one — not reconstructed at handover.</p></div><div class="step"><span class="n">02</span><h4>Coordinate</h4><p>One accountable team holds the information across all four service lines, on the Group operating stack.</p></div><div class="step"><span class="n">03</span><h4>Verify</h4><p>RAMS, method statements and inspection records checked against the audit posture used on Higher-Risk Buildings.</p></div><div class="step"><span class="n">04</span><h4>Hand over</h4><p>An audit-ready, structured information set the client and their PQQ teams can actually use.</p></div></div></section><section class="sec"><div class="intro2 reveal in" style="margin-bottom: 36px;"><div><div class="kicker">Accreditation wall</div><h2 class="dhead">What PQQ teams<br>scan for first.</h2></div><p class="body">The certifications that get a contractor through pre-qualification — held by AMPM Building Services or leveraged from the Group. We send the full pack with every PQQ response.</p></div><div class="acc-wall reveal in"><div class="cell"><span class="t">ISO 9001</span><span class="d">Quality management</span></div><div class="cell"><span class="t">ISO 14001</span><span class="d">Environmental management</span></div><div class="cell"><span class="t">ISO 45001</span><span class="d">Health &amp; safety</span></div><div class="cell"><span class="t">Constructionline</span><span class="d">Gold · via the Group</span></div><div class="cell"><span class="t">CHAS</span><span class="d">H&amp;S pre-qualification</span></div><div class="cell"><span class="t">SafeContractor</span><span class="d">Approved contractor</span></div><div class="cell"><span class="t">NICEIC</span><span class="d">Electrical contracting</span></div><div class="cell"><span class="t">Gas Safe</span><span class="d">Gas installation</span></div></div></section></div><section class="band ink" data-nav-dark="true"><div class="shell"><div class="intro2 reveal in"><div><div class="kicker on-dark">Inherited credibility</div><h2 class="dhead sm" style="color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">A quarter-century<br>of life-safety behind us.</h2></div><div><p class="body" style="color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.86);">Our sister company <strong style="color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Gemini AMPM</strong> has protected the South East's most demanding buildings — fire, security and passive fire — since 1997. Employee-owned, with NSI Gold, BAFE, FIRAS and Constructionline Gold among its accreditations.</p><p class="body" style="color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.86); margin-top: 14px;">For Building Services clients, that means the compliance posture, the audit framework and the operating stack are the Group's — not a new contractor's first attempt at them.</p><div class="cta-row2"><a class="btn ghost" href="https://geminiampm.co.uk" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Visit Gemini AMPM ↗</a></div></div></div></div></section><section class="band green" data-nav-dark="true"><div class="shell"><div class="cta-split reveal in"><div><div class="kicker on-dark">For PQQ teams</div><h2 class="dhead sm">Request our<br>compliance pack.</h2><p class="body" style="margin-top: 18px;">Accreditation certificates, insurance schedule, RAMS templates and our golden-thread method statement — sent to a named contact.</p></div><div class="cta-row2" style="flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start;"><a class="btn ghost" href="/contact/">Request the pack →</a><a class="btn ghost" href="/contact/">General enquiry</a></div></div></div></section></div><footer class="foot" data-nav-dark="true"><div class="foot-inner"><div><div class="fwm">AMPM</div><span class="fmer" aria-hidden="true"><span style="background: var(--m-green);"></span><span style="background: var(--m-purple);"></span><span style="background: var(--m-orange);"></span><span style="background: var(--m-blue);"></span></span><p class="ftag">MEPH, Commercial, Fabric and Groundworks — one accountable contractor for Londo